intro: From shadows to victory – become the ultimate warrior!
description:
A professional fighter, whose name is lost in the shadows, has been kidnapped by a mercenary and imprisoned in a dark basement. But nothing will break her will! Escaping captivity, she sets out on a relentless path toward the mastermind behind her assassination – a powerful boss hiding deep within his lair. To reach him, she must battle an entire army of elite fighters, just as skilled as she is.

Immerse yourself in dynamic combat. Wield a vast arsenal of melee weapons – from swords and katanas to nunchaku and other deadly tools. This is a game where your combat experience, agility, and weapon mastery will be the key to victory.
